cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper focuses on learning efficient representations from multimodal sequences, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
